[src:insecure-deserialization/deserialization-of-untrusted-data] The created JFrame object will have a “defaultCloseOperation” of value 3 – which indicates that the JVM should exit when this JFrame window is closed.
[src:insecure-deserialization/deserialization-of-untrusted-data] The next example is one that is much more likely to be seen in custom code.
