[src:insecure-deserialization/marshalling-computer-science] The unmarshal methods defined in the `jakarta.xml.bind.Unmarshaller` class are overloaded to accept XML from different types of input such as a `java.io.File`, `java.io.FileInputStream`, or `java.net.URL`.
